<i>noun</i>: 절도죄 [절또쬐/절또쮀], 절도 [절또], 도둑질 [도둑찔], 도난 [도난] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>절도죄 [절또쬐/절또쮀]</dt><br>
<dd>theft</dd><br>
<dd>남의 물건을 몰래 훔친 죄.</dd><br>
<dd>The crime of secretly stealing another person's belongings.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>절도 [절또]</dt><br>
<dd>theft</dd><br>
<dd>남의 물건을 몰래 훔침. 또는 그런 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of secretly stealing another person's belongings, or a person that commits such an act.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>도둑질 [도둑찔]</dt><br>
<dd>theft; stealing</dd><br>
<dd>남의 물건을 몰래 훔치거나 허락 없이 가지는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>Stealing or taking things belonging to others without their approval.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>도난 [도난]</dt><br>
<dd>theft; being robbed</dd><br>
<dd>도둑을 맞음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of being robbed.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>